msgid "<userinput>(?:PATTERN)</userinput> (Non-capturing group)"
msgstr "<userinput>(?!PATTERN)</userinput> (бһ”бһҠбһ·бһҹбҹҒбһ’вҖӢ lookahead)"

#. Tag: para
#: regular-expressions.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
